timeline.bodyText:
I know this isn't your code, but since you're here... this only tests the first value in invalidNamespace. What you need is something like
for (final String tn : invalidNamespace) {
  Assert.assertThrows(IllegalArgumentException.class, () -> TableName.isLegalFullyQualifiedTableName(Bytes.toBytes(tn)));
}

A bunch of these tests appear to make this mistake.

